{"tid":323792,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"港豬5大旅行壞習慣","createTime":"2017-07-16T01:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T06:45:29.000Z","uid":93485,"like":82,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"91e12bda7c904633a4113d0357e5e2e3c58f1ae6","tid":323792,"uid":93485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T01:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/094324_56dac5e540cd36304bec9e38b596364d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F094324_56dac5e540cd36304bec9e38b596364d.jpg&h=ff2ca4b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你咩，除左嘈同唔執枱係真係差<br />\n<br />\n買野計價錢又唔撚得<br />\n等人又唔撚得<br />\n開心興奮又唔撚得<br />\n去旅行去黎做乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野東方人容易興奮<br />\n見過啲鬼佬興奮未<br />\n<br />\n黃皮豬就是原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fULAR7_5alE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfULAR7_5alE&d=%2F5XvjiI4PBuk9itysjG%2BENr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=587d082f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fULAR7_5alE</a>"},{"pid":"dbff227ab78c7dc15e71034c6fc540ebe65d8813","tid":323792,"uid":1833,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T01:54:01.000Z","msg":"為屌而屌<br />\n計下價錢又屌<br />\n拎住旅遊書又屌<br />\n港豬就係原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378088875de1e00ff140d03475bea1d7e0fa04c5","tid":323792,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T01:58:37.000Z","msg":"鬼一樣"},{"pid":"52079815bca078a76a746a8502bb01ac2b2470cd","tid":323792,"uid":81507,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T02:54:37.000Z","msg":"嘈同埋無手尾係真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d38ad7ec01d4a1ac2a57f8445f59ef019de961d","tid":323792,"uid":53880,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T02:56:48.000Z","msg":"冇野搵