就企正門口位，出面行人路正中間咁等<br />\n其實喺出面企埋一邊等，大家都舒服</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港畜最仆街就係唔會識顧及其他人"},{"pid":"eae887a278a37a4db963f58663eac30e75d20cc5","tid":323792,"uid":71133,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:34:46.000Z","msg":"去親日本最嘈嘅一定係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8078e33100ef316e956c511c2f08a4008c55acb0","tid":323792,"uid":126436,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:35:54.000Z","msg":"駁乜柒 支那港豬鬼佬都好 影響到人就係錯架啦 on99 而家又唔係話剩係香港人先有 咁撚大反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41408996b6ba0de8787730601535a6b38cf7020e","tid":323792,"uid":73160,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:36:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去親日本最嘈嘅一定係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港真係最仆街<br />\n有文化嘅大陸人仲好d"},{"pid":"14a9fd5de5fef9f2fb6b73783bd12bd3bf498d18","tid":323792,"uid":84032,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:37:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東方人容易興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢點真係擺撚明佢見識少<br />\n當你未去過歐洲<br />\n去下老蘭就知啲白皮豬幾撚易發癲起哄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff054fd1f8daa66d69b54222957ff4d6ff5eec1","tid":323792,"uid":52026,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:37:36.000Z","msg":"香港人最大習慣<br />\n自視過高，覺得自己做好d就高人一等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ce6a60c817e265f07724448a6b576f53fbf726","tid":323792,"uid":54371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco